<h1 id="toc3"><span>The Tales</span></h1>
<p><strong>Stealing Solidarity</strong></p>
<p>These are the tales that serve as the basis of the canon: the escape of the Black Rabbit Company from the Foundation and the theft of SCP-2117.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/stealingsolidarityphase1">Phase 1</a><br />
